"""
Edwin O365 Connector — Microsoft Graph API
Modes:
  sync <source>   — incremental extraction to data/o365/
  <crud command>  — interactive CRUD (send email, create event, etc.)

Sources: mail, calendar, teams, sharepoint, onedrive, all
"""

